            <h2>üí° The Philosophy</h2>
            <p>
                These tools embody a core belief: <strong>AI isn't here to replace us‚Äîit's here to jam with us.</strong>
            </p>
            <p>
                Rather than treating AI as a faster search engine or productivity hack, this toolkit approaches AI collaboration 
                as genuine teamwork. Each tool is designed to make implicit work explicit, enable better human-AI collaboration, 
                and keep humans at the center.
            </p>
            <blockquote>
                "The best teams are human + AI, not human vs. AI."
